els scale toward trillions of parameters. These systems rely on agentic long‑term memory for context that persists across turns, tools, and sessions so agents can build on prior reasoning instead of starting from scratch on every request.</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/blog/introducing-nvidia-bluefield-4-powered-inference-context-memory-storage-platform-for-the-next-frontier-of-ai/\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\" target=\"_self\">Source</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
